                        <interp inst="t18491217-name-159" type="given" value="HENRY"></interp>HENRY TYLER</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, A</hi> 412). I produce a certificate—(<hi rend="italic">read—Emma Surridge, Convicted Jan.</hi>, 1847, <hi rend="italic">of stealing money from the person, and transported for ten years</hi>)—I was presents—she is the person—she got off transportation owing to her good conduct.</p>
